@hereforgoodish2 Many of these like $GRZ.V or $ASHM were risky, distressed assets, frozen because of Venezuelan government. 

Now that there's a regime change from Maduro, all of their value (gold mines, bonds) just got unlocked. 

For that reason, lot of these are not on Nasdaq / NYSE because of small marketcap or foreign companies with Venezuelan interest, so you would need to go to $IBKR or others to access then.
